{"tid":970350,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會愛一個人愛到成日心痛","createTime":"2019-01-05T17:43:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T18:46:59.000Z","uid":222576,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b5c3fdd6bd05d34a4c13c16ff5c02ceb13b74ca0","tid":970350,"uid":222576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:43:10.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意好鍾意我男朋友，所以好擔心佢有一日會唔愛我，會離開我。有時出完一日街之後會好唔捨得佢，個心會有少少痛。有時又會自己犯賤咁想像佢背後會同其他女仔出街或者whatsapp講曖昧嘢，跟住會搞到個心拿住痛。我拍過幾次拖未試過咁鍾意一個人，佢講少少嘢，做任何嘢都會牽動到我情緒。依家我地熱戀期冇咩爭吵，日日都好sweet，所以我大部份時間都好開心。但係我好怕過左依段時間之後，佢會開始冷淡，我真係好怕自己將來會受到傷害⋯⋯究竟我點樣先可以冇咁在乎？"},{"pid":"a104d31427f8dad7bb0862376fabdbcdd509061d","tid":970350,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:46:12.000Z","msg":"你過咗熱戀期就會冇咁care<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f433a4af5b0cdd9cb1bdf19c79e9b597565cfa59","tid":970350,"uid":222576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a104d31427f8dad7bb0862376fabdbcdd509061d","tid":970350,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:46:12.000Z","msg":"你過咗熱戀期就會冇咁care<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:49:27.000Z","msg":"希望係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6531a7f037dd6d18183f3ab25c5fc279cfc1d95","tid":970350,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T17:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.independent.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2016/10/10/23/heart-attack.jpg?w968h681\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.independent.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2016%2F10%2F10%2F